{"user":"U0401BVRA04","type":"message","ts":"1776430263.177379","client_msg_id":"cf7b6b73-a17b-4f08-82ba-72e243dc96f7","text":"HUGE breakthrough on Ravens this morning. Like I have spent the last month banging my head against the wall on how to tie up the last 5 chapters of this book, and this morning I FINALLY figured it out. I also wrote at 6 a.m. for the first time in foreeeever which felt amazing, and now that I've done the "figuring out" in my notebook I'm hoping I can get back onto some 6am prickles to draft those last five chapters out. After a very long, very sleepy winter I feel like my morning writer brain is FINALLY kicking back into gear and I am so, so excited to have the energy to get to the end of this draft!

Also, I was so in flow that Olivia woke HERSELF up and came into my room to tell me we were late for school. So let's also hype my kid for having better track of time than me :sweat_smile:","team":"T01NPHKSMA9","thread_ts":"1776430263.177379","reply_count":3,"reply_users_count":3,"latest_reply":"1776440012.778539","reply_users":["U049SSEC90T","U044SBPRH6C","U01NYR15VE0"],"is_locked":false,"subscribed":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"RZvb9","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"HUGE breakthrough on Ravens this morning. Like I have spent the last month banging my head against the wall on how to tie up the last 5 chapters of this book, and this morning I FINALLY figured it out. I also wrote at 6 a.m. for the first time in foreeeever which felt amazing, and now that I've done the "figuring out" in my notebook I'm hoping I can get back onto some 6am prickles to draft those last five chapters out. After a very long, very sleepy winter I feel like my morning writer brain is FINALLY kicking back into gear and I am so, so excited to have the energy to get to the end of this draft!

