{"user":"U042G2BTBK8","type":"message","ts":"1774976315.061739","client_msg_id":"196b8281-795c-42f7-8cfd-371130b27564","text":"So... I've been sitting on this for a few weeks but I was so nervous in the beginning I couldn't even think about it or talk about it. March 1st I queried my DREAM agent. Eleven days later she requested a full. On query tracker, you can see how many queries an agent gets, so I checked it out today just to see. In the past 3 months she's received about 607 queries. Out of all those, she's only requested 3 full manuscripts and mine is one of them. :face_holding_back_tears: I'm not a math genius but that's like 1 out of every 200 or 0.5% and I'm trying to be proud of myself in this moment. I've been so worried sick about her possibly saying no that I forgot to celebrate where I'm at right now and I just wanted to share it with people who get it. :crossed_fingers::heartpulse::smiling_face_with_3_hearts:

