{"user":"U05U0KY6KTL","type":"message","ts":"1775443703.527669","client_msg_id":"3CD85B29-B762-4B03-8495-BB5D3705E55C","text":"I just submitted a document to help the students at my former high school for their spring play. They're doing Harry Potter and the Cursed Child: School Edition and I asked my former director if he would like me to do a write up to help the cast and crew since they weren't born when the series began. Just doing all this research and writing for them made my heart so full because I love supporting the kids in that program any way I can. My high school they're department was truly life saving for me so giving back to them any way I can just brings me so much joy. 

The document is also 18 pages and over 3,000 words. ","team":"T01NPHKSMA9","thread_ts":"1775443703.527669","reply_count":1,"reply_users_count":1,"latest_reply":"1775473694.977679","reply_users":["U02EH242ARJ"],"is_locked":false,"subscribed":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"qAEPP","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"I just submitted a document to help the students at my former high school for their spring play. They're doing Harry Potter and the Cursed Child: School Edition and I asked my former director if he would like me to do a write up to help the cast and crew since they weren't born when the series began. Just doing all this research and writing for them made my heart so full because I love supporting the kids in that program any way I can. My high school they're department was truly life saving for me so giving back to them any way I can just brings me so much joy. 

The document is also 18 pages and over 3,000 words. "}]}]}],"reactions":[{"name":"heart_hands","users":["U03JN2L76NB","U08A1A5HCMU","U02EH242ARJ","U09T42KJV6E"],"count":4},{"name":"gem-heart","users":["U03JN2L76NB","U05QWLQQ3L3","U057A5E8N7J","U08A1A5HCMU","U02EH242ARJ","U04SWK60P1T"],"count":6},{"name":"face_holding_back_tears","users":["U03JN2L76NB","U05QWLQQ3L3","U08A1A5HCMU","U02EH242ARJ"],"count":4},{"name":"raised_hands","users":["U03JN2L76NB","U08A1A5HCMU","U02EH242ARJ"],"count":3},{"name":"heart_hands::skin-tone-2","users":["U05QWLQQ3L3","U04SWK60P1T"],"count":2},{"name":"hedgehog-joy","users":["U02EH242ARJ"],"count":1},{"name":"blob_aww","users":["U02EH242ARJ"],"count":1}]}

{"text":"I tend to stick to the same 3 coffee shops in my neighborhood because I'm a creature of habit and they're close by. But today they were literally ALL full so I had to go a little further afield to find a place to write (husband and kid are home today so focus time in our house is nonexistent :sweat_smile:). Anyways I found this tiiiiny hole-in-the-wall place about a 10 min drive from my house that I had no idea existed. It's run by an Iranian couple who set up a salon/coffee shop duo business. The husband was working the cafe today and he was so, so lovely and told me to stick around as long as I wanted. And also I was 100% convinced I died and went to heaven when I had a bite of the apple tart ... 

I think I found a cute new writing haunt and I'm so excited. Sitting in quiet coffee shops is basically my favourite thing to do, especially when they're as cute and the food as delicious as this one :blob_excited:","files":[{"id":"F0AQPJ06YTF","created":1775240494,"timestamp":1775240494,"mimetype":"image/jpeg","filetype":"jpg","pretty_type":"JPEG","user":"U0401BVRA04","user_team":"T01NPHKSMA9","editable":false,"size":1573799,"mode":"hosted","is_external":false,"external_type":"","is_public":true,"public_url_shared":false,"display_as_bot":false,"username":"","name":"20260403_122755.jpg","title":"20260403_122755.jpg","url_private":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF/20260403_122755.jpg","url_private_download":"https://files.slack.com/files-pri/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF/download/20260403_122755.jpg","media_display_type":"unknown","thumb_64":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_64.jpg","thumb_80":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_80.jpg","thumb_360":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_360.jpg","thumb_360_w":270,"thumb_360_h":360,"thumb_480":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_480.jpg","thumb_480_w":360,"thumb_480_h":480,"thumb_160":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_160.jpg","thumb_720":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_720.jpg","thumb_720_w":540,"thumb_720_h":720,"thumb_800":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_800.jpg","thumb_800_w":800,"thumb_800_h":1067,"thumb_960":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_960.jpg","thumb_960_w":720,"thumb_960_h":960,"thumb_1024":"https://files.slack.com/files-tmb/T01NPHKSMA9-F0AQPJ06YTF-37b1da12c2/20260403_122755_1024.jp